{"type": "article", "id": 45262, "title": "台湾啤酒出了好多“小鬼”包装，很可爱｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-09-17T23:23:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27927, "name": "台湾啤酒"}, {"id": 2347, "name": "宝丽来"}, {"id": 44124, "name": "Survival Capsule"}, {"id": 44125, "name": "Klipy Design"}, {"id": 44126, "name": "Spencer Merolla"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 96, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170918072342YLz4q6I2vA0Twjf8.png", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Coal Comforts by Spencer Merolla</h3><p>为气候变化发声不一定得走严肃的科普路线，最近美国艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.spencermerolla.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spencer Merolla</a> 就在组织一个让人眼前一亮的企划：快闪烘培店 Coal Comforts。她出售的曲奇饼干和各式蛋糕都是灰色的，但并不以“黑暗料理”为卖点——这些不能下肚甜点其实都是用煤炭制作而成的。Merolla 希望用这些每个人都熟悉的食物，引发人们对过度开发的反思。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/678640112/coal-comforts-a-climate-change-art-bakery\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从 25 起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917111953OHbWLZ8i1kXsEuo9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917111953zNUjR8CioBYJMA03.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917111954VLytoAKpRBD6GHSF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917111953LjI0FJilN8mXoQD4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.772059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917111954KVhloRvSDtzuET0k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>OneStep 2 I-Type by Polaroid</h3><p>为庆祝品牌创立 80 年，著名即时成像相机制造商宝丽来最近发布了 OneStep 系列第二代产品 OneStep 2 I-Type 拍立得相机，希望能够通过经典的设计重回市场。考虑到当下的拍摄习惯，OneStep 2 采用 USB 充电，机身配备了内置式闪光灯和一个计时器，可用于多人自拍。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112022g2BMphqe0JnmUrCj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.717604\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112021XxlyBkhIe6ACMUzc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112020Kcfai1SwhXbAuYzJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112023x1BVvX0wrnP6JNsM.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.806846\" data-format=\"png\">\n</figure></div><h3>Survival Capsule by Julian Sharpe &amp; Scott Hill</h3><p>2004 年的印度洋海啸夺走了 22.5 万人的生命，这起伤亡惨重的自然灾害使美国西雅图的航天工程师 Julian Sharpe 和 Scott Hill 开始思考：在难以及时开展撤离行动时，有没有可能让人们在救生舱度过危机？为此，他们联手创立了一家名为 <a href=\"http://survival-capsule.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Survival Capsule</a> 的公司，负责研发适用于家庭和公共场所的球形“方舟”。这些救生舱由航天级别的铝合金打造，分为五种不同尺寸，内部配备了椅子和储存食物的空间，最多可容纳 10 人在灾害时生存五天。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112154jx13b6ZOMdqhS7zs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112217M1o6pdeHGZKxc0WA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112217OtUqJ2xMlGDj0rPY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.266432\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><h3>Cake Divider by Klipy Design</h3><p>生活中难免会碰到一些考验友情的时刻：比如玩一局大富翁、UNO，或是分披萨和蛋糕。为了帮助人们均分食物，以色列工业设计公司 Klipy Design 推出了一款带刻度的辅助工具。只要将它插在披萨或是蛋糕正中央，转到对应的人数（分为 6、8、10 和 14 人四种），再用刀沿着指引槽切开即可。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B009MTT6R8/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 14.38 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709171122397cbFgjzA8nT1WMBD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.461538\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112239KhNXUm2DA3wEVYI6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.461538\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112240ZnzK13g4G2LVpofx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.461538\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Clippad by Giacomo Zangani</h3><p>想把智能手机变为小时候玩的掌上游戏机？意大利设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/giacomozangani\" rel=\"nofollow\">Giacomo Zangani</a> 带来的这款游戏手柄 Clippad 是个很容易引发怀旧情绪的概念设计。手柄通过蓝牙与手机相连，将两部分分开后就能分别固定在手机两侧，后方的夹子可以根据手机的厚度进行调节，因此号称能够适配大部分机型。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112254d5rTQh6knDGYZI3i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112254agZXPkbcJtsQGH8i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112254ojVsgXIFPvb5NxUc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.999167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112252gnywHab0XjopAZKP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.900000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Taiwan Beer by Haniboi</h3><p>今年中元节，台湾著名啤酒品牌“台啤”委托艺术家李翰（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HANIBOI/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Haniboi</a>）为其设计了一套限量版的“搞鬼罐”。围绕着“恶搞”这一主题，李翰决定把创作当作类似课本和拍立得相片上那些即兴发挥的涂鸦，设计了 6 个小鬼和收复他们的钟馗形象，透过他们与酒标的互动呈现出每个角色的性格。最终，台啤还委托李翰额外创作了以小鬼为主角的动画短片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112354KBGiVWt4XOaQqTNw.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.569004\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112351b5lYCn1fIXi3jWuG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709171123523zPqr58VSLWi6wnD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170917112351HXhqP1UkoOC5p3Ag.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709171123528pwVk2vK4A7cuJOH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>"}